"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
" Clear search highlight
"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
noremap <silent> <C-n> :nohl<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <C-n> :nohl<CR>
inoremap <silent> <C-n> <esc>:nohl<CR>
"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
